\id LUK Aruamu trans by Obnadum, Francis, Steven, Siria, Arnold; exegetical check by John/Marsha and all Aruamu translators; comprehension checked by 3 groups; consultant checked by Mike Sweeney and 6 Aruamus 1997. Revised by Aruamu translation team in 2019-2020, with input from many Aruamus. 
\h Luk 
\toc3 LU 
\toc2 Luk 
\toc1 Luk Osirizir Akar Aghuim 
\mt1 Luk Osirizir Akar Aghuim 
\mt2 O 
\mt1 Luk 
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim 
\ip Luk Osirizir Akar Aghuim…®n ak…®nafarim…®n aven, e Iesus…®n garima, a Israelian gumazamiziba ua me inigha, egha Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba, uaghan me ini. Iesus faragha uan ingangarim damuasa, kamagh…®n gumazamizibav m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod Akar Aghuim onganarazibagh amir gumazamizibav k…®nasa na m…®sevegha, borem nan dapanim ginge, kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ekiam…®n Duam nan iti.‚Äù (N…® Luk 4:18…®n gan.) Ez…® bar guizbang…®ra, ak…®nafarir kam…®n Luk Iesus geghara ghaze, a gumazamizir os…®mt…®zir av…®riba ateribar apangkuvigha derav…®ra me gami. 
\ip Bizir Iesus amiba, da an adarazigh amima, me bar a gakonge. Dughiar Maria a batezim…®n, gumazamiziba bar akonge. (N…® Luk 1:42-48 ko 2:10…®n gan.) Egha ghua ak…®nafarim g…®vaz…® nagh…®n tuz…®, Iesus God…®n Nguibam…®n ghuavanaboz…®ma, gumazamiziba bar akuegha mamagh…®ra iti. (N…® Luk 24:52…®n gan.) 
\ip Iesus…®n ik…®r…®m…®rim…®n bizir av…®riba, Luk uab…®ra dagh eghari. Bizir kaba, da ak…®nafarir igharazitam…®n itir puvat…®. Luk uab…®ra, Iesus nguazim…®n izezir bizir av…®rir otivizibagh eghari. Luk uab…®ra, a Iesus…®n akar is…®n zuir kam geghari, a kamak…®n: Gumazir mam os…®mt…®zim tuavim…®n a bato, ez…® Samarian gumazim an akura. Ez…® akar is…®n zuir igharazim, Luk a geghari, otarim afeziam ategha ghua tintinibar aruigha g…®n uamategha ize. Egha Luk Iesus…®n akar is…®n zuir mabanang uaghan dagh eghari. Egha Luk uab…®ra, bizir Sakius batozim geghari, kar gumazir dag…®aba isim. 
\ip Bizir maba Luk akar av…®riba dar iti, dar kara: God ko m…®k…®mv…®ra ikiamin arazim, ko God…®n Duam…®n ingangarim, ko God gumazamizibar arazir kuraba g…®n amadir arazim. Egha Luk uaghan amiziba ingarizir bizibar akar av…®riba da iti. 
\ip Luk…®n akaba, da ak…®nafarir kamra itir puvat…®. Luk uaghan ak…®nafarir igharazim osiri, e a d…®bora ghaze, Aposelbar Ingangaribar Ak…®nafarim. E fo, Iesus God…®n Nguibam…®n ghuavanabogha g…®vaz…®ma, Aposelba bizir av…®ribagh ami. Ez…® ak…®nafarir kam…®n aven, Luk aposelba amizir bizibar eghaghanim osiri. 
\c 1  
\ms1 Luk osirizir akar faragha zuim 
\mr (Sapta 1:1-4) 
\p  
\v 1-4 \x - \xo 1:1-4 \xt Jon 15:27; Aposel 1:1; 11:4; 15:28; Hibru 2:3; 1 Pita 5:1; 1 Jon 1:1\x*Gumazir aruam, Tiofilus, n…® fo, gumazamizir av…®riba God en tong…®n amizir bizibar ganigha, dar gun osirasava ami. E uari uan damazibar ganizir gumazamizibar akam baraki. Me faragha God…®n akam…®n ingangarir gumazamizibar otivigha, an akam akuri. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® uaghan akar kam osirigh n…® bagh anemangasa. Egha k…® deraghav…®ra dar m…®ngaribagh foghasa ingara ghua dagh foghava, n…® bagha bar derav…®rama da osiri. N…® dar gan fogh suam, bizir n…® oraghizir kaba da guiz…®n biziba. 
\ms1 Jon Gumazamiziba Ruer Gumazim…®n amebam a batezir dughiam ko Maria Iesus batezir dughiam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am 
\mr (Sapta 1:5--2:52) 
\s1 Ensel Sekaraian m…®g…®a ghaze, Jon otogham 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt 1 Eghaghaniba 24:10\x*Dughiar kam…®n Herot Judian atrivim…®n itima, God…®n ofa gamir gumazir mam…®n ziam Sekaraia, an Abiyan adarazir gumazir mam. Ez…® an amuim Elisabet, a Aron…®n ovavim.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Jenesis 17:1; 1 Atriviba 9:4; Aposel 23:1; Filipai 3:6\x*Aning bar deraghav…®ra God…®n Akar Gavgaviba ko bizir a damuasa e m…®kemeziba, aning dar g…®n zui. Ez…® God aning…®n garima, aning an damazim…®n bar dera.  
\v 7 Elisabet furabar iti, kamagh…®n amiz…® aning boriba puvat…®gha, dughiar ruarim pura ikia ghua bar ghuri. 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt 1 Eghaghaniba 24:19; 2 Eghaghaniba 8:14; 31:2\x*Ez…® dughiar mam…®n ofa gamir gumaziba ingarima, Sekaraia uaghan ofa gamir gumazim…®n m…®n God…®n damazim…®n ingari.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Ua Me Ini 30:7-8; 1 Samuel 2:28; 2 Eghaghaniba 29:11\x*Ez…® me God…®n D…®penim…®n ofa gamir gumazibar arazibar g…®nt…®gha, gumazim am…®s…®vasa me dag…®aba akuri. Ez…® God Sekaraia am…®sefe. Eght…® Sekaraia God…®n D…®penim…®n aven mang…® m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuim dapongam.\f + \fr 1:9 \ft Kar men arazim, God gumazim uan ingangarim bagh anem…®s…®vasa, me ikararer kam gami. Ikararer kam a Satun ikararer biziba iniasa ikararem…®n amir puvat…®.\f* 
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Ofa Gami 16:17; Akar Mogomem 8:3-4\x*Ez…® m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuim dapongamin dughiam otoz…®ma, gumazamizir God…®n ziam feba, God…®n D…®penim…®n m…®riam…®n uari akuvagha God ko m…®gei. 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Ekiam…®n Ensel a batogha, pauran mughuriar aghuim tuamin ofa gamir dakozim…®n agharir guvim…®n amadaghan tughav iti.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Gumazir Dapaniba 6:22; Daniel 10:8; Luk 1:29; Aposel 10:4\x*Ez…® Sekaraia an apigha d…®gavir kuram gamigha bar atiatingi.  
\v 13 Ez…® ensel kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúSekaraia, n…® atiatingan mark…®, n…® God ko m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®am, God a baraki. Ez…® n…®n amuim Elisabet n…® bagh otarim bategham. Eght…® n…® ziar kam, Jon a dat…®gh.  
\v 14-15 \x - \xo 1:14-15 \xt D…®boboniba 6:3; Gumazir Dapaniba 13:4; Jeremaia 1:5; Galesia 1:15\x*Egh n…® bar akuegh navir am…®rizim…®n ik…®. Eght…® a God…®n damazim…®n ziar ekiam iniam, kamagh…®n amiz…® gumazamizir av…®riba an otoghamin dughiam…®n bar akuegham. Eght…® a wain ko d…®par onganibar aman kogham. A uan amebam…®n navir averiam…®n aven ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…®, God…®n Duam bar a giz…®vagham.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Malakai 4:5-6\x*Egh a uam Israel…®n gumazamizir av…®riba inigh, men Ekiam God bagh mangam.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Malakai 3:1; 4:5-6; Matyu 11:14; 17:11-13; Mak 9:12\x*Eght…® Elaijan itir God…®n Duam ko gavgavir kamra Jon…®n ik…®t…®, a Ekiam…®n faragh mang…®va, afeziabar amut…® me ua uan boribagh ifuegh…®va, ak…®riba ragha God gasaraziba ua me damut…®, me ua n…®ghn…®zir aghuibar gumazamizibar amuva, egh gumazamizibav k…®mt…®ma me uari ak…®r…®ghas…®, egh Ekiam bagh m…®zuam ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Jenesis 18:11\x*Ez…® Sekaraia ensel…®n azara, ‚ÄúK…® ghuriz…®, nan amuim uaghan ghurigha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® manmagh…®n guizbang…®ra bizir kam g…®fogham?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Daniel 8:16; 9:21; Matyu 18:10; Hibru 1:14\x*Ez…® ensel an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® Gebriel. K…® God…®n damazim…®n tughav iti. God uab…® na amadaz…®ma, k…® akar aghuir kam…®n n…® m…®k…®masa ize.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Esekiel 3:26; 24:27; Luk 1:45\x*N…® nan akaba baregha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim dar itir puvat…®. Bizir kam bang…®n n…® m…®k…®man kogh mamagh…®ra ik…®t…®, bizir kaba otivamin dughiam otogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 21 Ensel Sekaraia m…®geima, gumazamiziba azenan ikia Sekaraia m…®zua ghuav am…®ragha pura n…®ghn…®si, manmagh…®n amiz…®ma, a dughiar ruarim…®n God…®n D…®penim…®n aven iti?  
\v 22 Ez…® an azenan otogha, me m…®k…®man asaghasaki. Ez…® me fo, a ti God…®n D…®penim…®n aven irebam…®n m…®n bizitam…®n gani. Egha an akam…®n me m…®geir puvat…®gha dafaribara me m…®gei. 
\p  
\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt 1 Eghaghaniba 9:25\x*Ez…® an ingangarir dughiam g…®vaz…®ma, a uan nguibam…®n ghu.  
\v 24 Dughiar maba ghua g…®vaz…®ma, an amuim Elisabet navim ada 5plan iak…®nibar uab…® modo.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 1:25 \xt Jenesis 30:23; Aisaia 4:1; 54:1; 54:4\x*Egha a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam na bagha bizir kam gami. A nan apangkuvigha nan aghums…®zim gumazamizibar damazim…®n anedangi.‚Äù 
\s1 Ensel Maria bagha akam inigha zui 
\p  
\v 26 Elisabet…®n navir adasem 6plan iak…®nim…®n otoz…®ma, God ensel Gebriel Nasaret…®n anemada, kar Galilin Distrigh…®n aven itir nguibar ekiam.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 1:27 \xt Matyu 1:18; Luk 2:5\x*Ez…® ensel ghua, guivir igiar gumazitam koma akuizir puvat…®zim bato, an ziam Maria, me gumazim Josep…®n ikiasa a ginaba. Josep, an Atrivim Devit…®n ovavimra.  
\v 28 \x - \xo 1:28 \xt Gumazir Dapaniba 6:12; Daniel 9:23; 10:19\x*Ensel a bagha ghua kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúDughiar aghuarim Maria. Ekiam n…® gifongegha derav…®ra n…® gamua egha n…® ko iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 29 Ez…® Maria an akam baregha d…®gavir kuram gamigha pura n…®ghn…®si, ‚ÄúKar akar manmagh…®n amizim?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 30 Ez…® ensel kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúMaria, n…® atiatingan mark…®, God bar n…® gifuegha n…® ko iti.  
\v 31 \x - \xo 1:31 \xt Aisaia 7:14; Matyu 1:21; Luk 2:21\x*N…® oragh, n…® navim asegh otarim bategh…®va, ziar kam Iesus, a dat…®gh.  
\v 32 \x - \xo 1:32 \xt Onger Akaba 132:11; Jeremaia 23:5; Mak 5:7\x*\x - \xo 1:32-33 \xt 2 Samuel 7:12-16; Aisaia 9:7\x*A ziar ekiam ik…®t…®, me suam, kar God…®n Bar P…®n Itim…®n otarim. Eght…® God a damight…®, a uan ovavim, Atrivim Devit…®n m…®n ikiam.  
\v 33 \x - \xo 1:33 \xt Daniel 2:44; 7:14; 7:27; Maika 4:7; Jon 12:34; Hibru 1:8\x*Eght…® a Jekop…®n adarazir atrivim…®n ik…®v…®ra ikiam. Eght…® a Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiar kam g…®vaghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 34 Ez…® Maria kamagh…®n ensel…®n azara, ‚ÄúK…® guivir igiar patam…®n itir puvat…®zim. Ez…® bizir kam manmagh…®n na batogham?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 35 \x - \xo 1:35 \xt Matyu 1:20; 14:33; Jon 1:34\x*Ez…® ensel an akam ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod…®n Duam n…® bagh izeght…® God…®n Bar P…®n Itim…®n gavgavim n…® avaragham. Eght…® borim God…®n damazim…®n zueght…® me God…®n Otarim a dar…®gham.  
\v 36-37 \x - \xo 1:36-37 \xt Jenesis 18:14; Jeremaia 32:17; Sekaraia 8:6; Matyu 19:26; Rom 4:21\x*Bizitam God…®n aven kozir puvat…®. N…®n anabam Elisabet, a ghuri, egha a uaghan navim adai. Me ghaze, a navim asangan kogham, ez…® an navir adasem dat…®r…®gh…®n iak…®nir 6plan tu.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 38 Ez…® Maria kamagh…®n ensel ikara, ‚ÄúK…® God…®n ingangarir amizim. N…® m…®kemezir mogh…®ra God bizibar na damu.‚Äù Ez…® ensel anetegha ghu. 
\s1 Maria Elisabet…®n ganasa zui 
\p  
\v 39 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Maria uan biziba ak…®righava, zuam…®ra nguibar ekiar Judian Distrigh…®n m…®ghs…®am…®n itim…®n ghu.  
\v 40 Egha a Sekaraian d…®penim…®n aven ghugha dughiam Elisabet gan…®ngi.  
\v 41 \x - \xo 1:41 \xt Luk 1:15\x*Ez…® Elisabet Marian tiarim barazima, an borim an navim…®n aven aguaghfa, ez…® God…®n Duam Elisabet giz…®fa.  
\v 42 \x - \xo 1:42 \xt God…®n Araziba 28:4; Gumazir Dapaniba 5:24\x*Ez…® a pamtem…®n tiarim akarigha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® amizibagh afiraz…® God bar bizir aghuim n…® gami. Egh a uaghan bizir aghuim borir n…® oteghamim gami.  
\v 43 Ez…® God tizim bagha derav…®ra na gami, ez…® nan Ekiam…®n amebam na bagh izi?  
\v 44 N…® dughiam na gan…®dima, k…® n…® barazir dughiamra, borir nan navir averiam…®n itim bar akuegha aguaghfa.  
\v 45 \x - \xo 1:45 \xt Luk 1:20\x*N…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n iti, ez…® Ekiam n…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®n bizibar n…® gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…® n…® bar akongegh.‚Äù 
\s1 Marian ighiam 
\p  
\v 46-49 \x - \xo 1:46-49 \xt 1 Samuel 2:1-10; Onger Akaba 34:2-3; 71:19; 111:9; 126:2-3; Habakuk 3:18\x*\x - \xo 1:46-55 \xt 1 Samuel 1:11; Onger Akaba 138:6; Malakai 3:12; Luk 1:25; 11:27\x*Ez…® Maria kamagh…®n m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúK…® pura Ekiam…®n ingangarir amizim, 
\q2 kamagh…®n amiz…®ma a na gin…®r…®. 
\q1 Kamagh…®n amiz…® nan navim Ekiam…®n ziam fe. 
\q2 Ez…® nan duam God bagha bar akonge, a nan akurvazim. 
\q1 God a bar gavgavigha bizir bar ekiabar na gami. 
\q2 Ez…® an ziam bar zuegha dera. 
\q1 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, dat…®r…®gh…®n tugh mang…® gumazamiziba na m…®k…®m suam, 
\q2 God derav…®ra n…® gami. 
\q1  
\v 50 \x - \xo 1:50 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:6; Onger Akaba 103:13-18\x*God gumazamizir an atiatiava an apengan itibar apangkufi. 
\q2 A kamagh…®ra dat…®r…®gh…®n itir gumazamizibar amu, 
\q3 egh g…®n izamin gumazamizibar amu mamagh…®ra ikiam. 
\q1  
\v 51 \x - \xo 1:51 \xt 2 Samuel 22:28; Onger Akaba 98:1; Aisaia 40:10; 1 Pita 5:5\x*A uan dafarim…®n bizir bar gavgavibagh ami. 
\q2 Gumazamizir uarira uan ziaba feba, 
\q3 a men ag…®raz…® me are. 
\q1  
\v 52 \x - \xo 1:52 \xt 1 Samuel 2:6; Jop 5:11; 12:19; Onger Akaba 147:6\x*God atrivibar gavgavim d…®kab…®ragha 
\q2 gumazamizir k…®niba fe. 
\q1  
\v 53 \x - \xo 1:53 \xt 1 Samuel 2:5; Onger Akaba 34:10; 107:9\x*A bizir aghuiba isava m…®tiriaba azibagh anigha, 
\q2 biziba bar iz…®vaziba amangiz…®ma me pura ghue. 
\q1  
\v 54-55 \x - \xo 1:54-55 \xt Jenesis 17:7; 17:19; 18:18; 22:17; Onger Akaba 98:3; 132:11; Aisaia 41:8; Maika 7:20; Rom 11:28; Galesia 3:16\x*A uan ingangarir gumazim Israel…®n akura. 
\q2 Egha en ovavibagh amizir Akar Gavgavim g…®n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra iti. 
\q1 Egha Abraham…®n apangkuvigha, 
\q2 g…®n otivamin gumazamizibar apangkuvigh mamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 56 Maria iak…®nir pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n Elisabet ko ikegha g…®n uamategh uan nguibam…®n ghu. 
\s1 Elisabet Jon batezir dughiam 
\p  
\v 57 Elisabet otamin dughiam otoz…®ma, an otarim bate.  
\v 58 An borogh…®ra itir darazi ko an anababa kamagh…®n oraki, Ekiam an apangkuvigha bizir aghuim…®n a gamiz…®, me a ko bar akonge.  
\v 59 \x - \xo 1:59 \xt Jenesis 17:12; Ofa Gami 12:3; Luk 2:21\x*Ez…® an 7plan arueba g…®vaz…®ma, me borim…®n m…®karzir mogomem…®n inim aghorasa izi. Egha me an afeziam…®n ziam Sekaraia a dar…®ghasa.  
\v 60 \x - \xo 1:60 \xt Luk 1:13\x*Ez…® an amebam kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúPuvat…®! E Jon a dar…®gham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 61 Ez…® me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n anabatam ziar katam itir puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 62 Egha me dafarimra an afeziam…®n azangs…®si, a ziar manatam uan otarim dar…®gham. 
\p  
\v 63 Ez…® Sekaraia an ziam osirasa biziba bagha dafaribara men azangs…®si. Egha kamagh…®n osiri, ‚ÄúAn ziam Jon.‚Äù Ez…® me kamagh…®n ganigha bar aguaghfa.  
\v 64 Ez…® an akam zuam…®ra kuiaghir…®z…®ma an m…®zem f…®riagh…®r…®z…®, a magh…®ra m…®g…®ava God…®n ziam fe.  
\v 65 Ez…® an borogh…®n itir darazi kamagh…®n ganigha, bar atiatingi. Ez…® Judian Distrigh…®n itir nguibar m…®ghs…®abar itibar gumazamiziba bizir otivizir kaba baregha dar gun uariv gei. 
\p  
\v 66 \x - \xo 1:66 \xt Jenesis 39:2; Onger Akaba 80:17; Aposel 11:21\x*Ekiam…®n gavgavim borir kam ko iti. Ez…® me bar mogh…®ra bizir kam baregha, a g…®n…®ghn…®gha a bagha azangs…®si, ‚ÄúBorir kam bar manmagh…®ram otogham?‚Äù 
\s1 Sekaraian ighiam 
\p  
\v 67 \x - \xo 1:67 \xt Joel 2:28\x*Ez…® an afeziam Sekaraia God…®n Duam a giz…®vaz…®ma, a God…®n n…®ghn…®zim…®n gun m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1  
\v 68 \x - \xo 1:68 \xt Onger Akaba 41:13; 72:18; 106:48; Luk 7:16\x*‚ÄúEkiam iza uan gumazamiziba ua me ini, 
\q2 kamagh…®n amiz…®, e an ziam fe, 
\q3 a Israelian God. 
\q1  
\v 69 \x - \xo 1:69 \xt Onger Akaba 18:2\x*God en akurvaghasa 
\q2 uan ingangarir gumazim Devit…®n adarazir aven gumazir bar gavgavim am…®sefe. 
\q1  
\v 70 \x - \xo 1:70 \xt Jeremaia 23:5-6; Daniel 9:24; Aposel 3:21; Rom 1:2\x*God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba 
\q2 bizir kam…®n gun fom…®ra kamagh…®n me m…®keme. 
\q1  
\v 71 \x - \xo 1:71 \xt Onger Akaba 106:10\x*An en apaniba ko en atara pazav e gamibar dafaribar e iniasa ize. 
\q1  
\v 72 \x - \xo 1:72 \xt Jenesis 17:1; 17:7; Ofa Gami 26:42; Onger Akaba 105:8-9; 106:45\x*Egh apangkuvim en ovavibar akakagh…®va, 
\q2 uan Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim gin…®r…®gham, 
\q3  
\v 73 \x - \xo 1:73 \xt Jenesis 22:16-17; Maika 7:20\x*Akar Gavgavir en ovavim Abraham gan…®ngizim. 
\q1  
\v 74 \x - \xo 1:74 \xt Rom 6:18; 6:22; Hibru 9:14\x*Egh en apanibar dafaribar uam e inigh, 
\q2 en amamangat…®ght…®, 
\q3 e an ingars…® atiatingan kogham. 
\q1  
\v 75 \x - \xo 1:75 \xt Efesus 4:24; 2 Timoti 1:9; Taitus 2:12-14; 1 Pita 1:15; 2 Pita 1:4\x*Egh an damazim…®n arazir aghuir a ifongezibar g…®n mang…®t…®, 
\q2 a ifongezir arazir aghuir kaba en ikiam. 
\q1  
\v 76 \x - \xo 1:76 \xt Aisaia 40:3; Malakai 3:1; 4:5; Matyu 3:3; 11:10\x*Ez…® n…® nan borim, n…® faragh mang…® Ekiam bagh tuavim ak…®r. 
