\v 80 \x - \xo 1:80 \xt Matyu 3:1; 11:7; Luk 2:40\x*Ez…® Jon g…®n aghua gavgaviz…®, an duam uaghan aghua gavgafi. A ghua Judian gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ikegha, g…®n Israel…®n gumazamizibar damazim…®n azenan oto. 
\c 2  
\s1 Maria Iesus bate 
