\p  
\v 1 Ez…® dughiar kam Sisar Ogastus akar gavgavim amadagha ghaze, ‚ÄúRom garir nguibabar gumazamiziba bar mang…® uan ziaba osir.‚Äù  
\v 2 Dughiar kam Kwirinius, a Sirian gumazir dapanim…®n itima, ziaba osirir dughiar faragha zuir kam oto.\f + \fr 2:2 \ft Dughiar kam, Rom…®n gavman Israelian nguibaba bar dagh ativagha dar gari. Israel…®n nguibar ekiam, a Provins Sirian aven iti. Rom…®n gavman…®n gumaziba, me men garir atriviba d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúSisar.‚Äù\f* 
