\v 4 Ez…® Josep uaghan Devit…®n anabar mam. Kamagh…®n amiz…® a Galilin Distrigh…®n itir nguibam Nasaret ategha, Judian Distrigh…®n itir nguibam Betlehem…®n zui, kar Devit…®n nguibam.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Luk 1:27\x*A mang…®va uan amuir inabazim Maria ko aning uan ziamning osirasa. Dughiar kam Maria borim…®n navim adai.  
\v 6 Egha aning ghua Betlehem…®n itima, Maria borim batamin dughiam oto.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Matyu 1:25\x*Ez…® a uan otarir ivariam bate. Egha inir av…®zibar borim nomke. Dughiar kam d…®penir akuim iz…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, aning borim isava bulmakauba apir danganim…®n anet…®. 
