\v 34 \x - \xo 2:34 \xt Aisaia 8:14; Hosea 14:9; Matyu 21:42; Aposel 28:22; Rom 9:32-33; 1 Korin 1:23; 1 Pita 2:7-8\x*Ez…® Simeon ghaze, God bizir aghuiba ia bagh dar amu, egha Simeon kamagh…®n an amebam Maria m…®gei, ‚ÄúBorir kam God a ginaba, eght…® Israel…®n av…®riba God bagh tugh gavgavigham. Eght…® av…®riba iregham. Eght…® gumazamiziba bizir an amibar gan…®va akar kurabar dav k…®mam.  
\v 35 \x - \xo 2:35 \xt Onger Akaba 42:10; Jon 19:25\x*Eght…® gumazir av…®ribar n…®ghn…®zir navim…®n aven itiba azenim giram. Eght…® os…®mt…®zir ekiatam uaghan n…®n navir averim…®n otivam, mati afuzim n…®n d…®ghorim m…®t…®.‚Äù 
