\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Aposel 2:37\x*Ez…® gumazamiziba Jon…®n azara, ‚ÄúEz…® e manmagh…®ra damuam?‚Äù  
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt Luk 11:41; 2 Korin 8:14; Jems 2:15-16; 1 Jon 3:17\x*Ez…® Jon me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir korotiar aven azuir pumuning itim, a tam is…® gumazir puvat…®zim dan…®ngigh. Ez…® dagheba itiba uaghan kamagh…®ra damu.‚Äù 
