\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt Matyu 21:32; Luk 7:29\x*Ez…® gavman…®n dag…®aba isir gumaziba uaghan ruasa ize. Egha me azangs…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúTisa, e manmagh…®ra damuam?‚Äù 
