\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Ua Me Ini 23:1; Ofa Gami 19:11\x*Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir maba Jon…®n azara, ‚ÄúEz…® eia, e manmagh…®n damuam?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® a me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazamizibar dag…®aba ok…®ms…®va, akar ifavaribar me gasan mark…®. Ia uan ingangarim…®n ivezimra init…® deragham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Gumazamiziba bizir kabar gara men navir averiaba me ginivima me pura n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, Jon ti God Ua Gumazamiziba Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim? 
