\p  
\v 21 Jon gumazamiziba ruer dughiam…®n, Jon uaghan Iesus rue. Ez…® Iesus uan afeziam God ko m…®geima, overiam kuiaghir…®z…®,  
\v 22 \x - \xo 3:22 \xt Jenesis 22:2; Onger Akaba 2:7; Aisaia 42:1; Matyu 3:17; 17:5; Mak 1:11; Luk 9:35; Jon 1:32\x*God…®n Duam bunbam…®n m…®n m…®ghegha izaghiri. Ez…® tiarir mam overiam…®n otogha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan Otarim. K…® guizbang…®ra n…® gifueghava n…® bagha bar akonge.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus…®n inaziba ko ovaviba 
