\v 15 Egha a God ko m…®geir d…®penibar men sure gamima, me bar an ziam fe. 
\s1 Nasaret…®n itir gumazamiziba  // Iesus…®n aghua 
\r (Matyu 13:53-58; Mak 6:1-6) 
\p  
\v 16 \x - \xo 4:16 \xt Matyu 2:23; Mak 6:1; Aposel 13:14; 17:2\x*Ez…® Iesus ikiava aghungiz…® nagh…®n Nasaret…®n ghu. Egha Sabat…®n dughiam…®n a God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven ghu, kar arazir a zuraram amim. A tugha God…®n Ak…®nafarim d…®ponasava ami.  
\v 17 Ez…® me God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Aisaian ak…®nafarir r…®ghizim a gan…®ngi. Ez…® Iesus ak…®nafarir r…®ghizir kam onegha, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n api: 
\b  
\q1  
\v 18-19 \x - \xo 4:18-19 \xt Aisaia 61:1-2\x*‚ÄúGod Akar Aghuim onganarazibagh amir gumazamizibav k…®nasa na m…®sevegha, 
\q2 borem nan dapanim ginge, 
\q3 kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ekiam…®n Duam nan iti. 
\q1 Egha uaghan akam akunasa na amada, 
\q2 eght…® k…® kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m suam, 
\q3 gumazir damazir kuraba ua ganam. 
\q1 Eght…® kalabus…®n itir gumazamiziba ko gumazir os…®mt…®zibar apengan itiba, 
\q2 k…® me bagh kalabus…®n tiar akam kuight…®, 
\q3 me kalabus ategh f…®righ…®regh mangam. 
\q1 K…® kamagh…®n me m…®k…®mam, 
\q2 Ekiam gumazamizibagh ifongezir dughiam, 
\q3 an otogha g…®fa.‚Äù 
