\p  
\v 42 Am…®nim tiraz…®ma, Iesus gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ghu. Ez…® gumazamiziba a buria ghua a batogha, an anogorogha ghaze, a me ategh mangan kogham.  
\v 43 \x - \xo 4:43 \xt Luk 8:1\x*Ez…® a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod Akar Aghuim akunasa na amada. Kamagh…®n amiz…® k…® nguibar igharaziba uaghan dar mang…® God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n Akar Aghuim akunam.‚Äù  
\v 44 \x - \xo 4:44 \xt Matyu 4:23\x*Egha a Judian Distrigh…®n God ko m…®geir d…®penibar akam akura ghuav…®ra iti. 
\c 5  
\s1 Iesus faragha diazir suren gumaziba 
\r (Matyu 4:18-22; Mak 1:16-20) 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 5:1-3 \xt Matyu 13:1-2; Mak 3:9-10; 4:1\x*Dughiar mam…®n Iesus Genesaret…®n d…®par akarer m…®riam…®n tughav itima, gumazamiziba anekuvagha God…®n akam barasi.\f + \fr 5:1 \ft Ziam ‚ÄúGenesaret,‚Äù a Galilin D…®par Akarem…®n ziar mam.\f* 
\v 2 Ez…® a d…®par m…®riam…®n garima, osiriba isir gumazibar bot…®n pumuning pura iti. Aning…®n ghuaviba uan iver ekiaba rue.  
\v 3 Ez…® Iesus bot…®n mam…®n ghuavanabo, kar Saimon…®n bot. Egha an azaragha ghaze, n…® tong a g…®s…®vaght…®ma a d…®par m…®riam atakigh. Ez…® a bot gaperaghav ikia gumazamizibar sure gami. 
\p  
