\v 5 \x - \xo 5:5 \xt Jon 21:3\x*Ez…® Saimon an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúEkiam, e d…®magarir kam…®n ingara ghua bar osiritam inizir puvat…®. Ez…® n…® m…®geima kamagh…®n k…® iver ekiaba akunam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 5:6 \xt Jon 21:6\x*Egha me Iesus m…®kemez…® mogh…®n amigha, osirir bar av…®riba iniz…®ma men iver ekiaba magh…®ra akarasava ami.  
\v 7 Ez…® me uan namakar bot…®n igharazim…®n itiba me gikariz…®ma me iza men akura, egha me iza bot…®n pumuning uaghara aning gaghuiz…®ma aning bar iz…®vagha osemegha magh…®ra d…®pam…®n ghuaghiri. 
\p  
\v 8-10 \x - \xo 5:8-10 \xt 2 Samuel 6:9; 1 Atriviba 17:18; Matyu 4:19\x*Ez…® Saimon Pita ko a ko iti darasi, me osirir me inizir kabar ganigha d…®gavir kuram gami. Saimon…®n roroamning Jems ko Jon, Sebedin otarimning. Aning Saimon ko ingarir gumazimning, aning uaghan d…®gavir kuram gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…® Saimon kamagh…®n ganigha, tevimning ap…®righa Iesus…®n suemning…®n borogh…®n ir…®. Egha ghaze, ‚ÄúEkiam, k…® gumazir arazir kurabagh amim! Kamagh…®n amiz…® n…® na ategh mang…®.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n Saimon m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® atiatingan mark…®, dat…®r…®gh…®n ikegh mang…®, n…® gumazamiziba iniam.‚Äù  
\v 11 \x - \xo 5:11 \xt Matyu 4:20; 19:27; Mak 1:18; Luk 18:28\x*Ez…® me uan botba m…®k…®rvegha, d…®par dadarim…®n ghuavanega, biziba bar da ategha Iesus…®n g…®n zui. 
\s1 Gumazir lepan ar…®mariam itim 
\r (Matyu 8:1-4; Mak 1:40-45) 
\p  
\v 12 Iesus nguibar ekiar mam…®n itima, gumazir mam lepan ar…®mariam bar aneg…®riz…®ma, a izava oto. Egha a Iesus…®n apigha ira uan guam nguazim m…®tuagha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® fuegh…®va na damight…®, k…® God…®n damazim…®n zuegh ua deraka.‚Äù\f + \fr 5:12 \ft N…® akar Matyu 8:2…®n itim…®n gan.\f* 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® Iesus uan agharim isa gumazir kam gat…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® ifonge. N…®n m…®karzim zuegh, ua deragh.‚Äù Ez…®ma lepan ar…®mariam zuam…®ra anetaki. 
\p  
\v 14 \x - \xo 5:14 \xt Ofa Gami 14:1-32\x*Egha Iesus akar gavgavim a gan…®ga ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® tav m…®k…®man mark…®. Egh mang…®, uab…® God…®n ofa gamir gumazim…®n akagh, egh Moses m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, n…® uab…® zueghs…® ofa damu. Eght…® gumazamiziba fogh suam, n…®n ar…®mariam g…®fa.‚Äù 
