\v 1 \x - \xo 8:1 \xt Luk 4:43\x*Bizir kabar g…®n, Iesus, nguibar ekiaba ko nguibar dozibagh arui, egha God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n akam akuri. Ez…® an suren gumazir 12pla uaghan an g…®n arui.  
