\v 16 \x - \xo 8:16 \xt Matyu 5:15; Luk 11:33\x*Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam lam gaborogha m…®nem…®n aven a modogha a isa dakozim…®n apengan anefazir puvat…®. An a inigh dakozim gis…®n anefagham, eght…® tina aven iz…®va angazangarim…®n ganam.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 8:17 \xt Matyu 10:26; Luk 12:2\x*Kamagh…®ra mogomer biziba da g…®n azenan otivigham. Eght…® bizir amigha aveziba da uaghan g…®n azenan otivigham.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 8:18 \xt Matyu 13:12; 25:29; Luk 19:26\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…® ia deraghv…®ra akar kam baragh. Gumazitam o amizitam God…®n akabagh foght…®, God uan akabar fofozir igharaziba a dan…®ngam, eght…® a God…®n akar av…®ribagh fogham. Eght…® God…®n akabagh foghan aghuazir gumazim o amizim, an fofozir muziarim God a dam a inigham.‚Äù 
\s1 Tinara a Iesus…®n amebam ko doziba? 
