\v 19 Ez…® Iesus…®n amebam ko doziba an ganasa izi. Ez…® gumazamiziba bar anekufa, kamagh…®n amiz…®, me an borogh…®ra mangan ibura.  
\v 20 Ez…® mav Iesus m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…®n amebam ko doziba muna azenan tuivighav ikia n…®n ganasa.‚Äù 
