\v 21 \x - \xo 8:21 \xt Luk 6:47; 11:28; Jon 14:21\x*Ez…® Iesus an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúTina God…®n akam baragha an g…®n zui, me nan amebam ko doziba.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus m…®geima am…®nir ekiam areme 
\r (Matyu 8:23-27; Mak 4:35-41) 
