\p Ez…® me atiatia, n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh amuava, uarira uarir azangs…®si, ‚ÄúKar gumazir manmagh…®n amizim? A m…®geima, am…®nim ko d…®pam an akam barasi!‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus gumazir mam…®n  // duar kuraba batoke 
