\v 32 \x - \xo 8:32 \xt Matyu 8:30; Mak 5:11\x*Dughiar kam…®n, dar b…®zir ekiar maba m…®ghs…®ar m…®riam…®n rogh…®ra ikiava api. Ez…® duar kuraba Iesus gakaghora ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® en amamangat…®ght…® e mang…® dar munabar aven mangeka.‚Äù Ez…® a men amamangat…®z…® me zui.  
\v 33 Ez…® duar kuraba gumazim ategha azenan iza dabar aven ghue. Ez…® dar b…®zir kam ara ghua davarir kuram giraghuegha d…®pam amegha ariaghire.  
\v 34 Ez…® dabar garir gumaziba garima bizir kaba otiviz…®, me ara ghua nguibar ekiam…®n bizir kabar gun m…®geima, nguibar azenan rogh…®ra itiba saram orasi.  
\v 35 Ez…® gumazamiziba ganasa izi, bizir tizimram oto? Egha me Iesus bagha iza garima, gumazir duar kuraba ategha azenan izezim, a Iesus…®n dagarim…®n m…®n aperaghav iti. A korotiaba aghuiz…® an n…®ghn…®zim ua dera. Kamagh…®n amiz…® me atiatingi.  
