\v 39 ‚ÄúN…® uamategh uan nguibam…®n mang…®, egh God n…® gamizir biziba bar me m…®k…®m.‚Äù Ez…® gumazim uamategha ghua nguibam garuava Iesus a gamizir biziba bar dar gun m…®gei. 
\s1 Iesus aremezir guivir mam gamiz…® a ua d…®kafi, egha amizir an korotiam…®n suirazim gamiz…®ma a ua dera 
\r (Matyu 9:18-26; Mak 5:21-43) 
\p  
\v 40 Iesus uamategha Galilin D…®par Akarem…®n vong…®n izez…®ma, gumazamiziba a iz…® me bativasa me a bagha oragha a m…®zua iti.  
\v 41-42 \x - \xo 8:41-42 \xt Matyu 9:18; Mak 5:22\x*Ez…® gumazir mam, an ziam Jairus, a God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n gumazir dapanim. An guivir vam…®ra an azenir 12plan borogh…®ra ghugha, aremeghasava ami. Kamagh…®n amiz…® a iza Iesus…®n dagarimning…®n borogh…®n ir…®. Egha uan d…®penim…®n mangasa Iesus gakaghori. Ez…® Iesus ghuav…®ra itima maburan av…®rim bar an okarigha kagh…®ra uari d…®kab…®ri.\f + \fr 8:41-42 \ft An guivir vam…®ra, a 12plan azenibar borogh…®ra ghu, kamagh…®n amiz…®, e ghaze, an azenir 12plan borogh…®ra ghu.\f* 
\v 43 Ez…® amizir 12plan azenibar ghuzim batir ar…®mariam itir mam, gumazitam an akuraght…® a deraghan kogham.  
\v 44 \x - \xo 8:44 \xt Matyu 9:20; Mak 5:28\x*A Iesus…®n g…®n izava an korotiar av…®zim…®n suiraz…®, an ghuzir ar…®mariam zuam…®ra dutugha ghu.  
\v 45 Ez…® Iesus azara, ‚ÄúTina nan suira?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® me bar uarir tiragha, ez…® Pita ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir Ekiam, gumazamiziba bar n…® akuvagha n…® adughadusi.‚Äù 
