\v 48 \x - \xo 8:48 \xt Luk 7:50\x*Ez…® Iesus a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúNan guivim, n…® navim bar am…®ragh ik…®. N…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim n…® gamiz…®ma n…® dera. N…® navir am…®rizim sara mang…®.‚Äù 
