\v 52 \x - \xo 8:52 \xt Luk 7:13; Jon 11:11-13\x*Dughiar kam…®n gumazamiziba bar, me uan evaribav sogha azia iti. 
\p Ez…® Iesus me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAzir akam atakigh. Guivim aremezir puvat…®. An akui.‚Äù  
