\v 54 \x - \xo 8:54 \xt Luk 7:14; Jon 11:43\x*Ez…® Iesus guivim…®n dafarim…®n suiragha a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúNan borim, n…® d…®kafigh!‚Äù  
\v 55 Ez…® an duam uamategha izez…®ma, a zuam…®ra d…®kavigha tu. 
