\v 56 \x - \xo 8:56 \xt Mak 7:36; Luk 5:14\x*Ez…® an amebam ko afeziam bar aguaghfa. Ez…® a kamagh…®n m…®g…®a aning ab…®ra, gua otozir bizir kam…®n gun gumazitam m…®k…®man mark…®. 
\c 9  
\s1 Iesus 12pla gumaziba amangi 
