\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 9:1 \xt Matyu 10:1; Mak 3:13-15\x*Iesus uan suren gumazir 12plan diaz…®ma, me a bagha izez…®, a duar kuraba batoghamin gavgavim ko gumazamiziba itir ar…®mariaba ak…®ramin gavgavim sara me gan…®ngi.  
\v 2 Egha me amaga ghaze, ia God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n akam akun, egh gumazamizibar ar…®mariaba ak…®rm…®ght…® me ua deragham.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 9:3-5 \xt Luk 10:4-11\x*Egha a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…®s…®va bizitam inian mark…®, m…®tariba, dagheba, dag…®aba, ko siot…®n ia g…®n daghuamin tam inian mark…®.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 9:4 \xt Matyu 10:11; Mak 6:10\x*Ia kamagh…®n damigh, d…®penir ia aven zuir manam, ia d…®penir kamra ik…®, mang…® dughiar ia nguibar kam atagh…®raghamim.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 9:5 \xt Matyu 10:14; Mak 6:11; Aposel 13:51\x*Eght…® gumazamiziba ia gifueghan koght…®, dughiar ia men nguibam atagh…®raghamim, ia uan dagaribar m…®neziba ap…®sigh, eght…® me fogh suam, arazir me amizir kam, a derazir puvat…®.‚Äù\f + \fr 9:5 \ft Judabar arazim kara, n…® me baraghan koght…®ma, me n…®n sagh, uan dagarir asuaba m…®neziba ap…®zigh…®va n…® ategh igharagh mangam. Ez…® en arazim kamak…®n, k…® n…® m…®k…®mt…® n…® na baraghan koght…®, k…® apem ap…®righ uan tuavim gighuvagh, suam, k…® n…®n sagham.\f* 
\v 6 \x - \xo 9:6 \xt Mak 6:12\x*Ez…® Iesus…®n suren gumaziba nguibabar ghuava, Akar Aghuim akura egha ar…®mariar gumazamizibagh amima me ghuamazi. 
\s1 Herot foghasa, Iesus a tinara 
