\p  
\v 7-8 \x - \xo 9:7-8 \xt Matyu 16:14; Mak 8:28; Luk 9:19\x*Ez…® Herot, gavman…®n dapanim, a bizir Iesus amiba baraghiz…®ma da ghuav…®ra iti. A fo, marazi ghaze, Jon aremegha ua d…®kafi, ez…® marazi ghaze, Elaija oto, ez…® marazi ghaze, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam fom…®ra ikegha aremegha ua d…®kafi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, Herot bar n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh ami.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 9:9 \xt Luk 23:8\x*Egha Herot kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® Jon…®n f…®rim atu. Ez…® tina bizir kabagh amima me dar gun m…®gei?‚Äù Egha a Iesus…®n ganasa. 
