\v 18 \x - \xo 9:18 \xt Matyu 16:13; Mak 8:27\x*Dughiar mam…®n Iesus uab…®ra Afeziam ko m…®geima, an suren gumaziba a ko itima, a men azara, ‚ÄúGumazamiziba tina na gar…®si?‚Äù 
