\v 22 \x - \xo 9:22 \xt Matyu 16:21; 17:22; Mak 8:31; 9:31; Luk 9:44; 18:32-33\x*Egha a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazamizibar Otarim bar m…®zazir ekiaba ko os…®mt…®ziba iniam. Eght…® Judabar gumazir aruaba koma ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba, ko Judan Arazibagh fozir gumaziba, me an aghuagh…®va a m…®sueght…® an aremegham. Egh dughiar m…®kezim…®n a ua d…®kavigham.‚Äù 
