\v 23 \x - \xo 9:23 \xt Matyu 10:38; 16:24; Mak 8:34; Luk 14:27\x*Egha a bar mogh…®ra me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazitam o amizitam nan g…®n iz…®s…®, a ifongezir biziba g…®n amadagh uan ter ighuvim zurara a gisaghpugh nan g…®n iz…®.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 9:24 \xt Matyu 10:39; Luk 17:33; Jon 12:25\x*Gumazamizir manam uan ik…®r…®m…®rim suiraghs…® n…®ghn…®ght…®, an ik…®r…®m…®rim g…®vagham. Eght…® gumazamizir manam na bagh uan ik…®r…®m…®rim ategh…®va, uan ik…®r…®m…®rim iniam.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 9:25 \xt Matyu 16:26; Mak 8:36\x*Gumazim o amizim nguazim…®n itir biziba bar da inigh, a g…®n oveght…®, bizir kaba manmagh…®n an akuragham? Bar puvat…®.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 9:26 \xt Matyu 10:33; Mak 8:38; Luk 12:9; 2 Timoti 2:12\x*Tina nan ziam ko nan Akar Aghuim…®n gun m…®k…®man aghums…®ght…®, g…®n Gumazamizibar Otarim uan afeziam…®n borogh…®n ikegh…®va God…®n damazim…®n zuezir enselba ko God…®n angazangarim sara izighir…®va, uaghan men aghums…®gham.  
\v 27 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ia kagh tuivighav itir darasi, ian tarazi oveghan kogham. Ia ik…®v…®ra ik…® gant…®ma, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam otogham.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus…®n m…®karzim igharagha gari 
