\p  
\v 28 \x - \xo 9:28-35 \xt 2 Pita 1:17-18\x*Iesus bizir kabav kemez…®, 8plan dughiaba g…®vaz…®ma, a g…®n Pita, ko Jon, ko Jems inigha me God ko m…®k…®masa m…®ghs…®ar ekiar mam…®n ghuavanabo.  
