\v 30 Gumazir pumuning, Moses ko Elaija,  
\v 31 \x - \xo 9:31 \xt Matyu 17:3; 17:9; Mak 9:4; 9:9; Luk 9:22; 13:33\x*aning Afeziar Ekiam…®n angazangarim…®n aven ikia, egha Iesus ko uariv gei. Me Iesus nguazir kam atagh…®ragham koma bizir a Jerusalem…®n damuamin bizibav gei.  
\v 32 \x - \xo 9:32 \xt Matyu 17:2-3; Mak 9:2-4; Jon 1:14; 2 Pita 1:16-18\x*Pita uan namakamning ko pariam men azima me akui, me osegha Iesus…®n angazangarir gavgavim…®n ganigha uaghan gumazir pumuning…®n gari, aning a ko tughav iti.\f + \fr 9:32 \ft Bizir otozir kam ti d…®magarim…®n oto.\f* 
\v 33 Ez…® gumazimning an atagh…®razima Pita kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, bar deragha e kagh iti! E purirpenir pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n ingaram. N…® bagh tam, Moses bagh tam, egh Elaija bagh tam.‚Äù (Pita akar kam m…®g…®a, egha uab…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar a m…®kemezir kam g…®fozir puvat…®.) 
