\v 35 \x - \xo 9:35 \xt Aisaia 42:1; Matyu 3:17; 12:18; 17:5; Mak 1:11; 9:7; Luk 3:22\x*Ez…® tiarir mam ghuariam…®n tong…®n otogha kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúKar nan Otarim, k…® a ginaba. Ia anar…®ram oragh!‚Äù  
\v 36 Tiarir kam m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, me Iesus…®n garima a uab…®ra iti. Ez…® Iesus…®n suren gumaziba bizir me ganizim…®n gun gumazitam m…®kemezir puvat…®. 
