\v 45 \x - \xo 9:45 \xt Mak 9:32; Luk 2:50; 18:34\x*Ez…® me m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®fozir puvat…®. A men modo, kamagh…®n amiz…® me a g…®fozir puvat…®gha an azangs…®ghan atiatingi. 
