\v 49 \x - \xo 9:49 \xt D…®boboniba 11:28; Mak 9:38\x*Ez…® Jon Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, e garima gumazir mam n…®n ziam…®n duar kuraba batosi. E fo, a en mav puvat…®, ez…® e an anogoroke.‚Äù 
