\c 10  
\s1 Iesus 72plan gumaziba amangiz…® me ghua an ingangarim gami 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 10:1 \xt Matyu 10:1; Mak 6:7\x*Egha bizir kabar g…®n Ekiam 72plan gumazir igharaziba m…®sevegha pumuning pumuning faragh nguibar ekiaba ko danganir a mangasa n…®ghn…®zibar me amadi.\f + \fr 10:1 \ft Fofozir gumazir av…®riba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, gumazir Iesus amadazibar d…®bobonim, a 72 puvat…®. Me ghaze, men d…®bobonim 70ra. Eght…® namba 70, a Luk 10:1…®n ik…®t…®, eght…® Luk 10:17 uaghan, namba 70 an ik…®.\f* 
\v 2 \x - \xo 10:2 \xt Matyu 9:37-38; Jon 4:35; 2 Tesalonika 3:1\x*Egha a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúDagher bar av…®rim anigha g…®vagha azenim…®n iti. Ez…® ingangarir gumazamizir da iniamin av…®riba puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia azenir kam…®n ghuavim…®n azangs…®ght…®, a ingangarir gumazamizibar amang…®t…®, me an azenim…®n mang…® dagheba iniam.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 10:3 \xt Matyu 10:16\x*Ia mang…®! K…® sipsip…®n nguziba afiar atiabar torim…®n iti mogh…®n ia amadaz…® ia zui.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 10:4 \xt 2 Atriviba 4:29\x*\x - \xo 10:4-11 \xt Matyu 10:7-14; Mak 6:8-11; Luk 9:3-5\x*Egh dag…®aba azuir m…®tarim ko beghiam ko dagarir asuaba inian mark…®. Eght…® gumazitam tuavim…®n ia batogh…®va dughiam ia dan…®ngt…®, ia a ikaraghan mark…®. 
\p  
\v 5 ‚ÄúEgh ia d…®penitam…®n aven mang…® egh faragh kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, navir am…®rizim ia ko iti.  
\v 6 Eght…® gumazir navir am…®rizim kagh ik…®t…®, ia navir am…®rizim an ik…®. Puvat…®ght…®, ian navir am…®rizim ua ia bagh izegham.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 10:7 \xt Matyu 10:10-11; 1 Korin 9:14; 10:27; 1 Timoti 5:18\x*Guizbang…®ra, ingangarir gumazamiziba uan ivezim isi. Kamagh…®n amiz…® ia d…®penir kam…®n aven ik…®, dagheba ko d…®par tizir me ia gan…®diba, ia dar am…®. Egh d…®penir mam…®n ikegh mam…®n mangan mark…®. 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 10:8 \xt 1 Korin 10:27\x*‚ÄúEgh ia nguibar ekiam…®n aven mang…®ght…®ma, me ia inigh tizim ia dan…®ngt…®, ia puram anem…®.  
\v 9 Egh ia ar…®mariaba itir darazir amight…® me ghuamagheght…®, ia kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam rogh…®ra ize.  
\v 10-11 \x - \xo 10:10-11 \xt Matyu 10:14; Luk 9:5; Aposel 13:51; 18:6\x*Egh ia nguibar ekiatam…®n aven mang…®t…®ma, me ia inighan koght…®ma, ia tuavir dozibar aven mang…® m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIan nguibar ekiam…®n nguaziba en dagaribar poghez…®, e da d…®si, eght…® ia kamagh…®n ganigh fogh suam, ia amizir arazir kam, a derazir puvat…®. Egh ia fogh suam, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam rogh…®ra ize.‚Äô  
\v 12 \x - \xo 10:12 \xt Jenesis 19:24-28; Matyu 10:15; 11:24\x*Ez…® k…® ia m…®gei, God…®n Kot…®n Dughiam…®n, os…®mt…®zir nguibar kam iniamim, an os…®mt…®zir Sodom inizim gafiragham.‚Äù 
\s1 Gumazamizir navim g…®razir puvat…®ziba bar ikuvigham 
\r (Matyu 11:20-24) 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 10:13 \xt Aisaia 23:1-18; Esekiel 26:1--28:26; Joel 3:4-8; Amos 1:9-10; Sekaraia 9:2-4; Matyu 11:21-23\x*Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n uan 72plan gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúIa Korasin…®n nguibam…®n itir gumazamiziba, iavzika! Ia kuram iniam. Ia Betsaidan nguibam…®n itir adarasi, Iavzika! Ia bar ikuvigham. Gumazitam Tair…®n nguibam ko Saidon…®n nguibam…®n ghua, mirakel…®n k…® amiziba men tong…®n dagh amighai, Tair ko Saidon…®n itir darazi ti fom…®ra navibagh iragha, azir adiariba aghuigha, averenim gapiava a gurua, egha uan arazir kam…®n uari akakagha ghaze, me uan arazir kuraba ataki.  
\v 14 God…®n Kot…®n Dughiam…®n, os…®mt…®zir ia iniamim, an os…®mt…®zir Tair ko Saidon iniamim gafiragham.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 10:15 \xt Aisaia 14:13-15\x*Ez…® ia Kaperneam…®n nguibam…®n itir darasi, ia ghaze, ia uari fegh God…®n Nguibam…®n ikiam, a? Bar puvat…®, God ia akunight…® ia Gumazamizir Oveaghuezibar Nguibam…®n mag…®ram. 
