\v 16 \x - \xo 10:16 \xt Matyu 10:40; Mak 9:37; Luk 9:48; Jon 5:23; 13:20\x*‚ÄúTina ia barasi a uaghan na barasi, tina ia barazir puvat…® a uaghan na barazir puvat…®. Egha tina na barazir puvat…®, a nan Afeziar na amadazim uaghan a barazir puvat…®.‚Äù 
