\v 18 \x - \xo 10:18 \xt Jon 12:31; 16:11; Akar Mogomem 9:1; 12:8-9\x*Ez…® a me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® Satan…®n garima a ira on…®marim…®n m…®n God…®n Nguibam…®n tagha g…®fa.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 10:19 \xt Onger Akaba 91:13; Mak 16:18; Aposel 28:5\x*Ez…® k…® gavgavim ia ganigha g…®fa, eght…® ia kuruziba ko tuighakabagh is…®n daruva da d…®k…®va, egh uan apanibar gavgavim a g…®vagham. Eght…® me bizir kuratam ia damuan iburagham.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 10:20 \xt Ua Me Ini 32:32; Aisaia 4:3; Daniel 12:1; Matyu 7:22; Filipai 4:3; Hibru 12:23; Akar Mogomem 3:5; 21:27\x*Eght…® duar kuraba ian akam m…®rara ghuzir bizim bagh akongan mark…®. God uan Nguibam…®n ian ziaba osirizir bizim bagh…®va ia akong.‚Äù 
