\p  
\v 21 Ez…® dughiar kamra, God…®n Duam Iesus gamima a bar akongegha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAfeziam, n…® nguazim ko overiam gativazir Ekiam! N…® fofozim ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itir gumazamiziba bizir kaba men modo, egha boribar m…®n itir gumazamizibar aka. Kamagh…®n amiz…® k…® n…® m…®naba. Guizbang…®ra Afeziam, n…® uan ifongiam…®n kamagh…®n ami.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 22 \x - \xo 10:22 \xt Matyu 28:18; Jon 1:18; 3:35; 10:15; 17:2\x*Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan Afeziam biziba bar da isa nan dafarim gat…®. Ez…® gumazitam Otarim g…®fozir puvat…®. Afeziam uab…®ra a g…®fo. Egha tav Afeziam g…®fozir puvat…®. Otarim uab…®ra, ko gumazir Otarim ifuegha Afeziam isa men akaziba, merara Afeziam g…®fo.‚Äù  
\v 23-24 \x - \xo 10:23-24 \xt Matyu 13:16-17; 1 Pita 1:10\x*Egha a ragha uan suren gumazibar gara kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, fom…®ra God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir av…®riba ko gumazamizir aghuir av…®riba, me ia dat…®r…®gh…®n garir bizibar ganamin ifongiar bar ekiam ikia, me dar ganizir puvat…®. Egha ia dat…®r…®gh…®n orazir akar kaba, me da baraghan ifongiar bar ekiam ikia, me tam baraghizir puvat…®. Ez…® ia, ian damaziba bizibar gari, kamagh…®n amiz…® ia bar akongegh!‚Äù 
