\v 25 \x - \xo 10:25 \xt Matyu 19:16; Luk 18:18\x*\x - \xo 10:25-28 \xt Matyu 22:35-40; Mak 12:28-34\x*Ez…® dughiar mam…®n, Judan Arazibagh fozir gumazir mam d…®kavigha Iesus gifarasa purama an azara, ‚ÄúTisa, k…® manmagh…®n damigh…®va zurazurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iniam?‚Äù 
