\v 27 \x - \xo 10:27 \xt Ofa Gami 19:18; God…®n Araziba 6:5\x*Ez…® an a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® uan Ekiam, a n…®n God, n…® bar uan navir averiam ko uan duam ko uan n…®ghn…®zim ko uan gavgavim sara bar a gifongegh. Egh uaghan, n…® uab…®ra uab…® gifongez…® mogh…®n, uan namakabagh ifongegh.‚Äù 
