\v 28 \x - \xo 10:28 \xt Ofa Gami 18:5; Nehemia 9:29; Esekiel 20:11-13; Rom 10:5; Galesia 3:12\x*Ez…® Iesus an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® bar deragha m…®gei. N…® mamagh…®ra damigh zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iniam.‚Äù 
