\v 30 Ez…® Iesus an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazim Jerusalem ateghava Jerikon uaghira, egha gumazir kuraba batoz…®ma, me an korotiaba suegha, puv…®ram a m…®sueghava are, egha anetaghiz…®ma a m…®k…®r…®gha ir…®ghav iti.  
