\v 33 \x - \xo 10:33 \xt Jon 4:9\x*\x - \xo 10:33-34 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 28:15\x*‚ÄúEz…®ma Samarian gumazir mam iza danganir gumazir kam itimra izava, an apighava bar an apangkufi.  
\v 34 Egha a bagha ghua wain ko borem an duaba ruegha da nomke. Egha a gumazim isa uan donki gis…®n anefagha, a inigha ghua daguir d…®penir mam…®n aven ghugha, derav…®ram a gami.  
\v 35 Egha am…®mzaraghan a dag…®ar pumuning d…®penir ghuavim ganigha ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® deragh an gan, eght…® dughiar k…® uamategh izamim, k…® iz…® bizir tizir n…® uam a gamiziba, k…® da ikaragham.‚Äô 
