\v 1 \x - \xo 12:1 \xt Matyu 16:6; 16:12; Mak 8:15\x*Ez…® dughiar kam…®n gumazamizir bar av…®rim uari akuvaghav ikia uari d…®kab…®ri. Ez…® Iesus magh…®ra uan suren gumaziba faragha dav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa uari bagh gan. Farisiba mati, yis bret…®n aven ghugha a gamiz…®ma a bar buiz…® mogh…®n ian aven mang…® ia gas…®ghas…®gham. Kamagh…®ra ifavarir araziba uaghan bar ia gas…®ghasigham.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 12:2 \xt Matyu 10:26; Mak 4:22; Luk 8:17\x*Moegha itir biziba, da azenim giregham. Akar aven itiba, gumazamiziba dagh fogham.  
