\v 27 \x - \xo 14:27 \xt Matyu 10:38; 16:24; Mak 8:34; Luk 9:23; 2 Timoti 3:12\x*Egh tina uan ter ighuvir an ovengamim a gupugh, egh nan g…®n izan kogh…®va, nan suren gumazim o amizim…®n otoghan kogham.\f + \fr 14:27 \ft N…® akar Matyu 10:38…®n itim…®n gan.\f* 
