\v 5-6 \x - \xo 15:5-6 \xt 1 Pita 2:10; 2:25\x*Egh an an apigh…®va bar akuegh a isi uan d…®p…®zim dat…®gh a gisaghpugh ngun mangam. Egh a uan namakaba ko an borogh…®n itir darazir diagh me akuvagh, egh kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòK…® uan sipsip…®n ovengezim uam an api! Ia iz…®. E a givarvaram.‚Äô  
