\p  
\v 22 ‚ÄúEz…® an afeziam kamagh…®n uan ingangarir gumazibav gei, ‚ÄòIa zuam…®ra! Korotiar bar aghuir ruarim inigh iz…®va a darugh. Egh ring an dafarim darugh, dagarir asuaba a daghuigh!  
\v 23-24 \x - \xo 15:23-24 \xt Luk 15:32; Efesus 2:1; 2:5; 5:14; Akar Mogomem 3:1\x*Nan borim aremegha ua angam…®ra iti. An ovengez…® e uam an api. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia mang…® bulmakaun nguzir m…®karzim sara itim a inigh iz…®va a m…®suegh e anem…®va a givarvaram.‚Äô Egha me a givarvara isam gami. 
