\v 27 \x - \xo 15:27 \xt Luk 15:2\x*‚ÄúEz…® a an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄòN…®n dozim uamategha ize. An aremezir puvat…®gha derav…®ra ikia uamatenge. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…®n afeziam a bagha bulmakaun nguzir m…®karzim sara itim m…®soke.‚Äô 
