\v 9 \x - \xo 16:9 \xt Daniel 4:27; Matyu 6:19-20; Luk 14:14; 1 Timoti 6:17-19\x*‚ÄúK…® ia m…®gei, ia nguazir kam…®n dag…®ar kuram, gumazamizibar akurvagh me ko namakabar amu. Eght…® dughiar da g…®vamim otoght…®, God n…® inight…® n…® mang…® ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiamin nguibam…®n mangam. 
