\v 10 \x - \xo 16:10 \xt Matyu 25:21; Luk 19:17-26\x*‚ÄúEgh tina bizir doziba deraghav…®ra dar gari, a uaghan bizir ekiaba deraghv…®ra dar ganam. Egha tina deraghav…®ra bizir dozibar garir puvat…®, a uaghan bizir ekiaba deraghav…®ra dar ganan kogham.  
