\v 13 \x - \xo 16:13 \xt Matyu 6:24\x*‚ÄúIngangarir gumazitam o amizitam, gumazir ekiar pumuning bagh ingaran kogham. A tav…®n aghuagh, tav gifuegham. O, a tav baghv…®ra ik…®, tav ak…®rim a gasaragham. Ia God ko dag…®aba bagh uaghara ingaran kogham.‚Äù 
