\v 50-51 \x - \xo 23:50-51 \xt Luk 2:25; 2:38\x*Ez…® gumazir mam, an ziam Josep, a Judian Provins…®n nguibam Arimatean ikegha ize. A gumazir aghuim, a God…®n damazim…®n arazir aghuibagh amir gumazim, egha a Judan kot…®n aven itir gumazir aruabar gumazir mam. Egha a men n…®ghn…®ziba ko arazibar g…®n mangan aghua. A God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam baghav…®ra m…®zua iti.  
\v 52 Egha Josep Iesus…®n kuam iniasa ghua Pailat…®n azaraz…®ma, Pailat an amamangat…®.  
\v 53 Ez…® a Iesus…®n kuam ter ighuvim…®n anedegha, inir ghurghurim…®n a righa, a inigha ghua dag…®ar torir me fom…®ra gumazir kuatam at…®zir puvat…®zim gat…®.  
\v 54 Kar dughiar bizibar k…®rim, ez…® Sabat…®n dughiam rogh…®ra ize. 
\p  
\v 55 \x - \xo 23:55 \xt Luk 23:49\x*Ez…® amizir Iesus…®n g…®n Galilin Distrigh…®n izeziba, me Josep…®n g…®n ghua dag…®ar torim…®n gari. Egha me uaghan garima, Josep manmagh…®n Iesus…®n kuam at…®.  
\v 56 \x - \xo 23:56 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:10; God…®n Araziba 5:14\x*Egha me ganigha g…®vaghava, uamategha uan d…®penibar ghua bizir mughuriaba itiba ko boreba isa da ar…®si. Egha God…®n osizirim m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, me Sabat…®n dughiam…®n avughsi. 
\c 24  
\s1 Iesus ua d…®kafi 
\r (Matyu 28:1-10; Mak 16:1-8; Jon 20:1-10) 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Sanden bar m…®zaraghara, amiziba borer mughuriar aghuir me ar…®ghiziba, inigha dag…®ar torim…®n zui.\f + \fr 24:1 \ft Wikbar faraghav…®ra zuir aruem, a Sandera.\f* 
\v 2 Egha me gari, torim avarazir dag…®am, me a puegha ghu.  
\v 3 Egha me aven ghua Iesus…®n kuam bagha garava avenge.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 24:4 \xt Aposel 1:10\x*Egha me kamagh…®n ganigha n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh amua tuivighav itima, gumazir pumuning zuam…®ra aning…®n korotiaba on…®marim…®n m…®n taghtagha men m…®n tughav iti.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 24:5 \xt Luk 2:9\x*Ez…® amiziba bar atiatigha avigha nguazim…®n gari, ez…® gumazimning kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha gumazir angam…®ra itim, gumazir ovengezibar danganim…®n a buri?  
\v 6 \x - \xo 24:6-7 \xt Matyu 16:21; 17:22-23; 20:18-19; Mak 8:31; 9:31; 10:33-34; Luk 9:22; 18:31-33\x*A kagh itir puvat…®; a ua d…®kafi! A ia ko Galilin ikia m…®kemezir bizim, ia a g…®n…®ghn…®gh,  
\v 7 ‚ÄòGumazamizibar Otarim, me a is…® gumazir arazir kurabagh amibar dafarim dat…®ght…®, me a is…® ter ighuvim…®n a guragham. Eght…® a dughiar m…®kezim…®n ua d…®kavigham.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù  
\v 8 Ez…® a m…®kemezir akaba, me dagh in…®r…®. 
\p  
\v 9 \x - \xo 24:9 \xt Mak 16:10\x*Egha me mozim ategha uamategha ghua bizir kabar gun Iesus…®n suren gumazir 11plan m…®g…®ava igharaz darazi sara m…®keme.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 24:10 \xt Luk 8:3\x*Amizir bizir kabar gun Iesus…®n 11plan aposelba ko igharaz daraziv kemeziba. Makdalan nguibam…®n amizim Maria, ko Joana, ko Maria a Jems…®n amebam, ko amizir igharazir maba uaghan me ko ikia bizir kabar gun aposelbav gei.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 24:11 \xt Mak 16:11; Luk 24:25\x*Ez…® me amizibav g…®a ghaze, me ti onganighama, kamagh…®n amiz…® me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim men akabar itir puvat…®.  
\v 12 Pita kamagh…®n oregha d…®kavigha ivegha mozim…®n ghu. Egha an aviragha, mozim…®n aven gara bizitam…®n apizir puvat…®gha inir ghurghuribara gari da ireghav iti. Egha a uamategha ghua n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh amua ghaze, kar manmagh…®n amizir bizim.\f + \fr 24:12 \ft Fofozir gumazir maba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, vez…®n kam…®n akaba, Luk uab…® da osirizir puvat…®. Gumazir igharazir mam g…®n da osiri.\f* 
