\v 19 \x - \xo 24:19 \xt Matyu 21:11; Jon 6:14; Aposel 2:22\x*Ez…® Iesus aning…®n azara, ‚ÄúBizir tiziba?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® aning a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGa Nasaret…®n Iesus bativizir bizibav gei. A God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam, ez…® an akaba ko ingangariba God ko gumazamizibar damazim…®n bar gavgafi.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 24:20 \xt Luk 23:1; Aposel 13:27-28\x*Ez…® en ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko en gumazir aruaba a isa gavman…®n dafarim gat…®z…®, me a m…®soghez…® an areme, ez…® me ter ighuvim…®n anegura.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 24:21 \xt Luk 1:68; 2:38; 19:11; Aposel 1:6\x*Ez…® e faragha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim kamagh…®n an iti, a God Ua Israelia Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim. 
\p ‚ÄúEz…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar mam ua iti, bizir kaba otivigha g…®vaz…®, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n an aremezir dughiar m…®kezim oto.  
\v 22-23 \x - \xo 24:22-23 \xt Matyu 28:8; Mak 16:10; Luk 24:1-11; Jon 20:18\x*Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n en amizir maba m…®zaraghara mozim…®n ghuegha an kuam…®n apizir puvat…®. Egha me iza e m…®kemez…®, e bar aguaghfa. Me ghaze, e irebam…®n m…®n enselbar garima, me kamagh…®n e m…®g…®a ghaze, a ua d…®kafi.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 24:24 \xt Jon 20:3-10\x*Ez…® en marazi mozim…®n ghuegha amiziba m…®kemez…® mogh…®n bizibar gari da iti, ez…® me an apizir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 25 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua gumazir onganimning! Gua God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n akaba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ko navim zuam…®rama dar itir puvat…®.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 24:26 \xt Luk 9:22; 24:44; Aposel 17:3; 1 Pita 1:11\x*Ez…® gua ti fozir puvat…®? God Ua Gumazamiziba Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim, faragh m…®zaziba inigh egh g…®n God…®n damazim…®n ziar ekiam iniam.‚Äù  
\v 27 \x - \xo 24:27 \xt Jenesis 3:15; D…®boboniba 21:9; God…®n Araziba 18:15; Onger Akaba 22:1-21; Aisaia 7:14; 53:7; Daniel 9:24; Malakai 3:1\x*Egha Iesus aning geghari. A faragha Moses osirizir akabav g…®a, ghua, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar akaba bar aning m…®gei. A God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n itir akar an gun m…®kemeziba, dar m…®ngariba bar aning…®n sure gami. 
