\v 30 \x - \xo 24:30 \xt Matyu 14:19; Luk 22:19\x*Egha Iesus damasa aning koma aperaghav ikia, bret inigha Afeziar Ekiam m…®nabagha, bret abigha aning gan…®di. 
\p  
\v 31 Ez…® aning dat…®r…®gh…®n an gara a g…®fofozima, a pura puvat…®.  
\v 32 Ez…® aning magh…®ra uaning m…®gei, ‚ÄúA tuavim…®n ga batogha God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n akabar ga m…®geima, gan navimning d…®kafi.‚Äù 
