\v 33 Egha aning d…®kavigha zuam…®ra uamategha Jerusalem…®n ghua garima, Iesus…®n 11pla suren gumaziba, me marazi ko uari akuvagha iti.  
\v 34 \x - \xo 24:34 \xt 1 Korin 15:4-5\x*Egha me kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra! Iesus aremegha d…®kavigha ghua Saimon bato!‚Äù  
\v 35 Ez…® aning magh…®ra tuavim…®n otivizir bizibar gun me m…®g…®a ghaze, a bret ab…®ghiz…®ma ga an ganighava a g…®fo. 
