\v 36 \x - \xo 24:36 \xt 1 Korin 15:5\x*Iesus…®n suren gumazir 11pla ko marasi, bizir kabar gun uariv geima, Iesus pura men tong…®n tughav ikia, kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúNavir am…®rizim ia ko ik…®.‚Äù\f + \fr 24:36 \ft Fofozir gumazir maba ghaze, vez…®n kam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir abuananam, Luk uab…® an osirizir puvat…®. Gumazir igharazir mam g…®n da osiri.\f* 
\v 37 \x - \xo 24:37 \xt Matyu 14:26\x*Ez…® me bar atiatigha ghaze, me duam…®n gari. 
