\v 47 \x - \xo 24:47 \xt Aisaia 49:6; 49:22; Jeremaia 31:34; Maika 4:2; Malakai 1:11; Matyu 28:19; 1 Timoti 3:16\x*Eght…® nan ziam…®n, ia nan akam inigh mangam. Ia Jerusalem ikegh nan akam inigh nguazim…®n m…®kebaba bar dar mang…®. Ia ik…®ziba bar dar gumazamizibav k…®mt…®, me navibagh iraght…® k…® men arazir kuraba g…®n amangam.  
