\v 49 \x - \xo 24:49 \xt Aisaia 44:3; Joel 2:28; Jon 14:16; 14:26; 15:26; 16:7; Aposel 1:4\x*Ia oragh. Afeziam faragha akam ak…®ra ghaze, a uan Duam is…® ia dan…®ngam. Ez…® k…® a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, ia bagh anemangam. Kamagh…®n ia nguibar ekiam…®n ik…®. Egh mamagh…®ra ik…® mang…® dughiar God ko itir gavgavim izighir…®t…®ma, ia a iniam.‚Äù 
